next semester, but I'm gonna try to stay.

00:49:59.746 --> 00:50:03.032
-Okay. It goes on. More of those.
-There's more of those.

00:50:03.099 --> 00:50:04.017
Jeez.

00:50:04.084 --> 00:50:06.494
And I'll show you
some of the fraternity houses.

00:50:06.561 --> 00:50:08.713
That's our on-campus hotel.

00:50:08.780 --> 00:50:10.513
-On-campus hotel?
-Yep.

00:50:11.058 --> 00:50:13.403
