00:50:13.470 --> 00:50:17.134
-The Sam Walton College of Business
is a ranked business school.

00:50:17.201 --> 00:50:19.926
Specifically, our supply chain program
is number one.

00:50:19.993 --> 00:50:22.643
-Supply chain program?
-We have a supply chain degree.

00:50:22.710 --> 00:50:25.127
