00:50:25.194 --> 00:50:27.076
So this is part of the flywheel.

00:50:27.503 --> 00:50:29.881
Get kids into university here.

00:50:29.948 --> 00:50:31.528
Get them into work at Walmart.

00:50:31.595 --> 00:50:32.933
