00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:36.457
-I mean, supply chain program.
-Yeah. It's very relevant to this area.

00:50:36.524 --> 00:50:40.404
-Here's a frat house. 
-They don't look as nice. The frat houses.

00:50:40.471 --> 00:50:43.476
