01:05:28.839 --> 01:05:30.439
[chopping]

01:05:32.360 --> 01:05:34.553
-CBR.
-Chopped burnt ends on there.

01:05:34.620 --> 01:05:36.484
Jacob, you're the man today.
Bring me around.

01:05:36.551 --> 01:05:38.929
-Really nice.
-Anytime you want to come back.

01:05:38.996 --> 01:05:41.152
