01:09:34.631 --> 01:09:36.470
I like 90s alt rock.

01:09:36.537 --> 01:09:38.563
I'm, like, an early 2000s girl.

01:09:38.630 --> 01:09:40.593
I've been listening to a lot of indie.

01:09:40.660 --> 01:09:43.206
I feel like whatever I grew up on
