01:10:05.788 --> 01:10:07.969
Come visit Arkansas. We have a great state.

01:10:08.036 --> 01:10:10.323
Not just Northwest Arkansas,
but the whole state.

01:10:10.390 --> 01:10:12.291
-Okay.
-It's a beautiful place.

